  "short_description": "THIS GAME IS NO LONGER BEING DEVELOPED, DO NOT DOWNLOAD IT. This page is here only to help the former devs and artists find new jobs in the industry.Hunt For Gods was a competitive, non pay-to-win, hero shooter game in which each of the 3 teams is led by a strategic player named God.",
