m_assets/steam/apps/576940/extras/eced13f5792dfffbff81dbcecda8c5c1.mp4?t=1718997544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Friends make everything better. In Hunt For Gods, you can team up with your friends and play together vs. other players or bots.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576940/extras/169ce9ab8b4a5f142381427b0545105e.poster.avif?t=1718997544\" width=624 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576940/extras/169ce9ab8b4a5f142381427b0545105e.webm?t=1718997544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576940/extras/169ce9ab8b4a5f142381427b0545105e.mp4?t=1718997544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As a God, you lead real humans instead of just bots. You can finally show who the real leader is after all these years spent playing RTS games.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576940/extras/dde5cf4a6d76be31ba4b111f4513204b.poster.avif?t=1718997544\" width=622 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576940/extras/dde5cf4a6d76be31ba4b111f4513204b.webm?t=1718997544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/576940/extras/dde5cf4a6d76be31ba4b111f4513204b.mp4?t=1718997544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There's no respawn, so it's GAME OVER as soon as you die. As an Hunter, your priority is to stay alive and crash your enemies before they crash you. You'll have to use all your skills and masteries to stay alive. Are you ready for the challenge?<br><br>15 players, 3 teams, one rule: get the pages and survive.",
